WebPart.Title: Appropriate Use Statement
WebPart.Description: Allows authors to enter rich text content.
WebPart.Content: This site is provided by Grant Thornton LLP as a means to enable efficient project and engagement management. Only relevant and appropriate business content is to be posted on the site. The content posted on this site is subject to periodic monitoring by the system administrator. Documents subject to retention are to be saved to the appropriate long-term repository. Other content will be permanently deleted at the termination of the project. Users have the responsibility to keep client lists, log-in passwords and other information strictly confidential.
